{"ID":"20260609133027-0m28las","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260609133027-0m28las","title":"2020年全国Ⅱ卷","type":"doc","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260609133027-h9s5wod","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133027-h9s5wod","updated":"20260609133058"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"1899年发现的殷墟甲骨文，是近代中国史料“四大发现”之一。殷墟甲骨文内容丰富，甲骨刻辞大多是占卜的记录，但占卜的范围很广，涉及祭祀、征伐、农业，田猎、气象、疾病等等，能够在一定程度上反映商代的社会生活。从目前的发掘情况看，甲骨文不止出现在殷墟，在北京、山西、陕西、山东、湖北，"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"宁夏都发现了刻有卜辞的甲骨。殷墟甲骨文年代最早，数量最多。但它不是当时唯一的文字。《尚书·多士》记载“惟殷先人，有册有典”，甲骨文有“典”“册” “聿(笔)”这样的文字，说明殷人祖先常规的书写材料是简册，书写工具是毛笔。只是用竹木做成的简册"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"腐烂，似乎无法在北方的地下长期保存，所以至今"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"没有发现商代的竹简。从出土材料看，甲骨文是商代晚期商王武丁以后才出现的，而商代早期、中期的青铜器上已有少量铭文。（  ），甲骨文字体简化较多。"},{"Type":"NodeTextMark","TextMarkType":"u","TextMarkTextContent":"对于文字本身来说，汉代学者总结的“六书”的方法在甲骨文基本都已出现，已经说明它是成熟的文字。"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"文字本质上是记录语言的，"},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeBackslash","Data":"span","Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"_"}]},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"受书写材质和体裁所限，甲骨文不能全面记录当时的语言现象，但是已经能够反映汉语的基本语法、词汇系统，"}]},{"ID":"20260609133027-ud9hl1i","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609133027-ud9hl1i","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"题目"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-zpv9zn4","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-zpv9zn4","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．依次填入文中横线上的词语，全都恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-nqqwgkt","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-nqqwgkt","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．以及   容易   尚且   然而"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-wmoxrb3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-wmoxrb3","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．乃至   容易   仍然   虽然"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-7ogm2yx","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-7ogm2yx","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．以及   易于   仍然   然而"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-o2xipc8","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-o2xipc8","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．乃至   易于   尚且   虽然"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-k93zqyn","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-k93zqyn","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．下列填入文中括号内的语句，衔接最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-2tx8t5x","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-2tx8t5x","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．由于相较于铸造的青铜器铭文，用刀在龟甲和兽骨上刻字比较困难"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-hkcx8gy","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-hkcx8gy","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．用刀在龟甲和兽骨上刻字比较困难，这是相较于铸造青铜器铭文而言的"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-qht6l5q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-qht6l5q","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．由于用刀在龟甲和兽骨上刻字比较困难，所以相较于铸造的青铜器铭文"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-qdc4243","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-qdc4243","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．用刀在龟甲和兽骨上刻字，相较于铸造青铜器铭文而言，比较困难"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-hqjopsk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-hqjopsk","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．文中画横线的句子有语病，下列修改最恰当的一项是（   ）"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-2zrsdqm","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-2zrsdqm","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"A．就文字本身来说，汉代学者总结的“六书”的方法在甲骨文基本都已出现，已经说明它是成熟的文字。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-4h2ib00","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-4h2ib00","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"B．对于文字本身来说，汉代学者总结的“六书”的方法在甲骨文中基本都已出现，已经说明它是成熟的文字。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-308h0vu","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-308h0vu","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C．对于文字本身来说，汉代学者总结的“六书”的方法在甲骨文基本都已出现，说明它已经是成熟的文字。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133110-rnbjbiw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133110-rnbjbiw","updated":"20260609133110"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"D．就文字本身来说，汉代学者总结的“六书”的方法在甲骨文中基本都已出现，说明它已经是成熟的文字。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133027-0paoikq","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609133027-0paoikq","updated":"20260609133120"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"答案"}]},{"ID":"20260609133027-ker09kp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133027-ker09kp","updated":"20260609133120"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．B    18．C    19．D"}]},{"ID":"20260609133027-6o6pwgd","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20260609133027-6o6pwgd","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"解析"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-2t5yual","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-2t5yual","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"17．本题主要考查正确使用词语（包括熟语）的能力。此类试题解答的关键在于两点：一是仔细审查该词语的语言环境，二是注意对近义成语的分析辨别。辨析近义成语的关键就是要仔细分辨它们的细微差别。首先阅读语境，把握语境含义，然后抓住相异语素，分析其意义差异，同时可联系日常习惯用语，推断词语意义及用法。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-dl8gbjj","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-dl8gbjj","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“以及”，连词，表示在时间、范围上的延伸；连接并列的词、词组或短句。“乃至”，连词。连接并列词语，表示事情所达到的范围，相当于“甚至”。语境中是“宁夏”是相对偏远的地方，应选“乃至”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-z2olygc","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-z2olygc","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“容易”，发生某种变化的可能性大。“易于”，指可能性很大。语境中说竹简腐烂的可能性很大，选哪个都可以。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-7qki45l","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-7qki45l","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“尚且”，副词，表示依旧、仍然。“仍然”，表示情况持续不变或恢复原状。语境是说至今没有发现商代的竹简，表示情况持续，选“仍然”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-0em2ure","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-0em2ure","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"“虽然”，用在上半句，下半句多用“但是”、“可是”、“却”等与它呼应，表示承认前边的事，但后边的并不因此而不成立。“然而”，从另一方面来说，表示转折关系。语境中后面有“但是”，可知应选“虽然”。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-hnz1x24","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-hnz1x24","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选B。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-cto1qwi","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-cto1qwi","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"18．本题主要考查语言表达简明、连贯、得体、准确、鲜明、生动的能力，重点考查语言的连贯能力。此类试题解答时，最重要的方法就是根据上下文意进行推断。命题者在题干所给文段中挖掉一句话，然后设计四个内容差不多、但句式各异的句子，选出最恰当的一项。选项都有一定的干扰性，难度适中。语句衔接补写，主要考虑上下文语境和语段的中心思想。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-zh2ecqk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-zh2ecqk","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"根据后面的文字“甲骨文字体简化较多”，可以推知括号里是写甲骨文相对于铭文简化的原因，因此句式选用“由于……所以……”更好，且主语应当是“甲骨文”，排除BD项；句子强调的应当是在龟甲兽骨上刻字困难，所以相较于铭文来说，甲骨文的字体简化较多，A项把“相较于铸造的铭文”放在前面不恰当，排除A项。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-wkz3xvw","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-wkz3xvw","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选C。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-5aldwg7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-5aldwg7","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"19．本题考查辨析并修改病句的能力。此类试题答题时应先浏览选项，排除有明显错误标志的句子，然后按照主谓宾的成分压缩句子，先观察主干部分，是否存在搭配不当、残缺等问题，再分析修饰成分。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-t1t5d5q","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-t1t5d5q","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"原句语病有：“对于文字本身来说”句式杂糅，应当改成“对于文字本身”或“就文字本身来说”，排除BC项；“在甲骨文”一句成分残缺，应在后面加上“中”，即“在甲骨文中”，排除AC项；“已经说明它是成熟的文字”中“已经”语序不当，放到“它”后面，排除AB项。"}]},{"ID":"20260609133132-n27hzbp","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260609133132-n27hzbp","updated":"20260609133132"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"故选D。"}]}]}